{"tid":2059062,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"罷食雲桂香！！！7日代通知金都唔撚找數仲要報狗！！！","createTime":"2020-06-10T15:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T05:53:54.000Z","uid":203397,"like":83,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"779732aece71ff9df2f719d7d61fde592414b5e3","tid":2059062,"uid":203397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:16:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1519297638229932/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1076113639215003%2Fposts%2F1519297638229932%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=fde11f24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1076113639215003/posts/1519297638229932/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n罷食雲桂香<br />\n<br />\n早前返旺角雲桂香追討既工友，佢既LAST PAYMENT只有人工同假期錢，仍未收到代通知金（7日啫，咁都走數！）<br />\n齊齊罷食雲桂香，香港各區分店如下：<br />\n<br />\n九龍：<br />\n旺角西洋菜街2W號1樓<br />\n觀塘牛頭角道343號地舖<br />\n大角咀埃華街56-58號地下<br />\n尖沙咀厚福街9號豪華閣地下1層<br />\n太子西洋菜南街101號金德行地下AB舖<br />\n長沙灣元州街393號地舖<br />\n<br />\n新界：<br />\n荃灣路德圍22號地舖<br />\n葵芳信芳街10 號月波樓地下E號舖<br />\n屯門仁政街26- 40號富恆樓地下<br />\n沙田正街偉華中心地下4號<br />\n大埔安泰路大埔廣場地下59號舖<br />\n<br />\n港島：<br />\n銅鑼灣駱克道450號地舖<br />\n<br />\n前文提要（事主返舖頭追討直播） ：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MvNWFt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MvNWFt&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=e1c9c1ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MvNWFt</a><br />\n<br />\n#雲桂香 #罷食 #直接追討 #藍店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGuhCzA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGuhCzA.jpg&h=24246dda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"643b9b4642be96d1ed6cefdb8aa18be22ad6ae43","tid":2059062,"uid":22974,"like":37,"dislike":4,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2753557e123313cb2810df05bf9c21a78db08dd5","tid":2059062,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:17:42.000Z","m